Healing From the Core, Full Body Presence, and Continuum & the Healing Process





A short message from Suzanne about our Products






Read a transcript of this videoThanks for checking out our products page.
We have something for almost everyone. There is downloadable audio as well as actual hard copy CDs you can purchase of all my Healing From the Core work. There’s my book, Full Body Presence on audio, read by me, as well as the eBook version which is downloadable right now.
For viewing pleasure and learning – we have hours and hours of DVD sets, with actual class room footage of Emilie Conrad and myself teaching together across 13 years – spanning a huge range of topics from things like how to work successfully with trauma, two DVD sets – two different classes – on creating more resilience in your immune system, a healthy visual system, the essence of the heart and lots more. We did our best to bring you the hands on magic of CranioSacral touch, combined with Emilie’s brilliance on movement, breath and sound. So, browse around! Every month we run a sale on one of the DVD sets – check out which one we have for sale this month. Save $50 month after month. If you don’t see what you want – let us know!
And, enjoy!
~Suzanne Scurlock-Durana





Welcome! Use the tabs below to browse our selection of books, CDs, DVDs and MP3 downloads. If you are a first time visitor to our site, you may find the following helpful:

Healing From the Core (HFC) products complement both Suzanne’s popular book Full Body Presence, as well as courses in the HFC curriculum. Anyone, anywhere can use these products to bring more full body presence into their lives!
Continuum and the Healing Process DVD sets chronicle 13 years of joint, annual instruction by Suzanne Scurlock-Durana and Emilie Conrad on a variety of topics. Learn more here or by viewing the tab below.




