View Full Screen (VIDEO)





Now Available for Pre-Order at Amazon and Barnes & Noble!
Reclaiming Your Body:
Healing from Trauma and Awakening to Your Body’s Wisdom
At one level or another, traumatic experiences are a part of any life — from the emotional shock of a parent or peer’s careless words in childhood to intense physical injuries to life-threatening emergencies and/or assaults. Not only do these events take a toll on our psyches, in Reclaiming Your Body: Healing from Trauma and Awakening to Your Body’s Wisdom (New World Library, June 14, 2017), author Suzanne Scurlock-Durana explains how they they cut us off from the wisdom of our bodies as well.
Learn More and watch a video about the book!














Full Body Presence by Suzanne Scurlock-Durana








   Amazon    Paperback Book $14.95
Add To Cart AudioBook + Explorations (MP3) $19.95
Add To Cart eBook (PDF) + Audio Explorations (MP3) $8.99






Includes free MP3 download of three Audio Explorations, or buy them on CD
View Full Screen





This book teaches “how to” become a steady presence for healing – yours and others. Knowing how to develop a strong, reliable therapeutic presence is a vital skill for anyone in care-giving or in health care today. For leaders and coaches this presence is vital for effective, creative problem solving and strong leadership. The included audio has three guided explorations for self-healing and developing full body presence – you’ll learn everything from how to take a baseline measure of where you are in any given moment; to how to fill and nourish yourself in a healthy manner; all the way to how to meet and disarm your own internal resistance to being fully present - so you can feel your freedom and fluidity to manifest more of what you want in your world.














Release & Renewal








Add To Cart Audio CD set $35.00
Add To Cart MP3 Download $14.45





View Full Screen





This two CD audio set grew out of Suzanne's annual trips to Sedona at the start of each New Year. This set provides a structure for those who want to create positive change in their lives, or are at a new beginning point. You can use it individually or in a group. It will assist you in integrating all facets of your life - your inner relationship with yourself, your connection to your spiritual life, family and community, career, creativity, abundance, health, power, sexuality and the ability to forgive and let go. The structure uses thought provoking questions and time for journaling with the exquisitely beautiful flute music of Jesse Kalu in the background. This process helps open the channels of intuition and communication, which are fundamental for successfully moving through all of life’s transitions and new beginnings.
CD and MP3 Download: 17 tracks, 1 hour, 46 minutes.














The Essence of the Heart








Add To Cart DVD set $300.00
SALE! Only $250 through the month of July (Save $50!)






2006 Continuum and the Healing Process DVD set
Emilie Conrad & Suzanne Scurlock-Durana





View Full Screen





Filmed in Reston Virginia, October 27-31, 2006
This professionally filmed DVD series offers a profound look at the essence of the heart and its contribution to living joyfully. In our culture today, the brain is often thought to be the dominant factor controlling our quality of life. While the brain may be responsible for maintaining the neurological connections of daily life, the heart is the master of what is most important. Our sense of connection to life, compassion and love, patience and forgiveness all come from an open, healthy heart. Emilie presents breath and intrinsic movement sequences as they relate to the heart. Suzanne presents the anatomy, inner guided explorations, and hands-on protocols. Come away with a deeper, clearer connection to your own heart, as well as how to hold a healing space for another.
DVD format: 9 DVDs per set for 20 hours of instruction





