This year's workshop has received rave reviews. We brought the process of moving deeply into the body using breath, sound, and movement together with specific protocols and explorations in the actual visual system. Many people had startling and wonderful results in their vision and experienced greater relaxation due to the improvement.
DVD format: 9 DVDs per set for 18 hours of instruction














